/*
    The caster slays a number of HD worth of creatures
    equal to 1d4 times level.  The creature gets a
    Fort Save or dies.
*/
//:://////////////////////////////////////////////
//:: Created By: Preston Watamaniuk
//:: Created On: June 1, 2001
